name: A fairy tail of Istanbul series...
description:
Istanbul is a great old city and millions of people have lived there. Also there were some magical moments with the inhabitants of the ancient world are can still be seen. 

In this project I tried to imagine all theese memories with a historical and supernatural flow. Photomanipulation and collage methods with old people and hero images were used on in this process. Living with old neighbours in Istanbul like a fairy tail. 

A fairy tail of Istanbul.
